@author Connor Doyle <connor.p.d@gmail.com>

Use Apache Ant to compile the project.
 1. Install the Scala programming language on the system, if you haven't already. 
 2. Edit the scala.home property in build.xml to point to your scala installation.
 3. Run ant in this directory
